She looked up at Drillbit, "Feeling better?" She smiled at him and 
sighed.  She was glad that they were still together.


Feline::
She followed HotRod into the chamber and closed the door behind them.



-----Original message-------
::DrillBit::

He activated his comm, to KitKat.
"I'm out side. I'll be right there." He ran inside, and to KitKat.
"You called, my love?"

::Hot Rod::

He walked to a CR, and opened it. He looked back at her, and winked.
